{"tid":2128074,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"赤巴 帶你翻去2019年7月28號","createTime":"2020-07-27T16:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T02:12:49.000Z","uid":238660,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d89f541887dfdd90b4009e4269bcf490c987250d","tid":2128074,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/28/005052_0be1675190f32d7c0084b03d61fe0e4a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F28%2F005052_0be1675190f32d7c0084b03d61fe0e4a.jpeg&h=e3e8b3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/07/28/005110_8a7411fc728b1e1b2885c1c8a5a62197.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F07%2F28%2F005110_8a7411fc728b1e1b2885c1c8a5a62197.jpeg&h=3fe1c653&s={SIZE}\" />[/left]728又係咩日子？ 赤巴記得呢一日原本係將軍澳排緊遊行，但係727所發生嘅曱甴恐襲令香港人憤怒，於是讓路比元朗，改咗期去8月4號，而呢個又係另一個故事。 <br />\n<br />\n今日嘅故事係咩？就係呢張圖，唔知作為香港人嘅你對佢有冇印象呢？喺呢日嘅元朗同樣係戰火連天。<br />\n<br />\n呢張圖就係當日就係手足嘅鐵盾俾海綿彈射穿咗，我記得當日有記者問佢係咩令你堅持到而家？手足嘅答案只有八個字：光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n呢一次革命唔係講笑，香港人冇得再輸，請香港人唔好再鬥黃，唔好再互屌。我唔想見到2014年嘅香港人。光復香港，時代革命呢八個字，已經唔係一個口號，係手足用血用汗去同政府博弈，係手足犧牲自己前途甚至生命換翻嚟嘅一個承諾，係只屬於香港人嘅革命。<br />\n<br />\n呢段歷史必定名垂千古，而我赤巴亦會致力記載住呢段香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港人嘅歷史<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n#728歷史"},{"pid":"8d7112f18be701a91928b47ce70994f349f09579","tid":2128074,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c51cefce4beab92779adeb11929e88de8fc1d12c","tid":2128074,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a93959acb3d5786e92175a7eb9b9185a12406af","tid":2128074,"uid":283182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime